item.description:
Hello photographers!

The meeting Begins at 7:30 PM the Last Thursday of every month. So from 7:30 to 8:00 will be open and social! Hanging out chit chatting will be encouraged!

The from 8:00 to 9:00 we will have a more organized agenda. A topic, a presentation, a group sharing of images, something related to Photography!

Then from 9 to 9:30 We will hang out again catching up with folks from that evenings topic. We'll clean up and head out by 9:45.

This months discussion topic: Photo Projects
I am looking for two more volunteers to share their photo projects with us. Right now I have two folks who have offered to share. They will each get 10-15 mins to share their project. It can be with digital files on the projector, a book we can pass around, or prints, a portfolio of work... Tell us about your project in 10 mins or less.
After everyone has shared we'll break out into groups and you can answer folks questions one on one.

If you would like to share your story. Email me directly with "Photo Projects" in the Subject line. donna @ erbphoto.com Tell me about your project and how you'd like to share it. I'll get back to you with details.

Cheers,
Donna
